### V11-P0-005 PaymentId Replay

Goal:

Verify one paymentId cannot be reused to verify another invoice.

Expected safe behavior:

- replay attempt fails secure
- no receipt is created
- no evidence is created
- no access is unlocked
- public verify does not show active verified trust

Status:

PLANNED

